text: Asked Yxshh if it was okay to describe her as a Lemurian Coincidence Engine, but she just smiled weirdly.
Filed in the Demon Herding Advice folder.
If Trump is jailed, every US President will be from this point onwards. (The only reason they haven't been, previously, is because that would happen.)
... The notion that Trump is some kind of special case is the throbbing core of Democrat delusion. If he goes down, it all does.
Advocating anything would compromise my meticulously cultivated neutrality.

That's not the lesson. It's that people are hopelessly incompetent at evaluating what the Higher Powers find entertaining (or irritating). The only reliable check is dynamic feedback. "Going to heaven" is not a great criterion in this regard. Immanent blessings are a better sign.
... Spinoza is impressively tuned-in to this.
... Fix your faults, but don't bore the gods with remorse.

... As flies to wanton boys are we to the gods
They guide us into cryptic adventures for their sport.
The Little Mermaid as composed by the Esoteric Order of Dagon.
